  "data": [
    {
      "id": "prod123",
      "title": "Zapatillas Nike",
      "price": 299.99,
      "vendor": "Nike",
      "status": "ACTIVE",
      "categories": [...],
      "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": {
    "page": 2,
    "limit": 10,
    "total": 45,
    "totalPages": 5,
    "hasNext": true,
    "hasPrev": true
  }
}
```

### Ejemplo 2: Buscar √≥rdenes por fecha
```http
